Login: ssh xxx     (xx@133.9.67.171   xx@133.9.8.197)
Make file: mkdir /home/xx
Data transmission: scp Desktop/xx xx@xx:/home/xx
Delete: rm -r /home/xx
Stick-up: cp /xx/xx /home/xx
List: ls
Get root: sudo -I

Backstage:
-Screen:
screen -ls
screen -r xx


-Tmux
tmux new -s demo (make new window)
tmux attach (enter window)
tmux detach (exit windos)
ctrl+b+d (exit server and keep tmux work)


GPU:
who 
nvidia-smi

